title: Looking for a 3v3 mate/team
body:
Hey, I'm looking for a 3v3 mate/team 2 seasons ago I was playing 3v3 in D3 but haven't played that much this year. So now I'm trying to get back to my cap. Currently, I'm P4 solo and G3 in 3v3, so a lot to do :D.
Add me if you're interested.
See you in Twisted Treeline ;)
Cheers
SF Captndittsche
